# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# LkSGCompass — Environment Variables
# Copy to .env and fill in your values
# NEVER commit .env to git
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── Backend ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# PostgreSQL connection string
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://lksg:CHANGE_ME@db:5432/lksg

# JWT secret — generate with: openssl rand -hex 32
JWT_SECRET=CHANGE_ME_USE_OPENSSL_RAND_HEX_32

# Server port
PORT=4000

# ── AI ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Anthropic Claude (for AI assistant tab)
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-api03-...

# ── Email ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Resend.com for transactional email
RESEND_API_KEY=re_...
RESEND_FROM=LkSGCompass <noreply@lksgcompass.de>

# ── URLs ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
FRONTEND_URL=https://lksgcompass.de
PUBLIC_APP_URL=https://lksgcompass.de
CORS_ORIGIN=https://lksgcompass.de,https://www.lksgcompass.de
APP_VERSION=v80

# ── Frontend (Vercel/Next.js) ─────────────────────────────
# Must be set at build time for Next.js
# Local development:
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:4000
# Production (Railway):
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://api.lksgcompass.de

# PostHog analytics (optional)
NEXT_PUBLIC_POSTHOG_KEY=phc_...
NEXT_PUBLIC_POSTHOG_HOST=https://eu.posthog.com

# ── Stripe billing (optional) ────────────────────────────
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_live_...
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_...
NEXT_PUBLIC_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_live_...
STRIPE_FREE_PRICE_ID=
STRIPE_PRO_PRICE_ID=price_...
STRIPE_ENTERPRISE_PRICE_ID=price_...

# ── File storage (optional) ──────────────────────────────
# Supabase Storage for evidence files
SUPABASE_URL=https://xxx.supabase.co
SUPABASE_SERVICE_KEY=eyJ...
EVIDENCE_BUCKET=evidence

# ── Demo account ─────────────────────────────────────────
DEMO_EMAIL=demo@lksgcompass.com
DEMO_PASSWORD=demo12345
